details: "Barbie Girl" is a song by the Danish-Norwegian dance-pop group Aqua. It was released in May 1997. The song topped the charts worldwide.

challenge.prompt: Complete the lyrics of Barbie Girl by Aqua.
challenge.text:
♫ I'm a Barbie girl, in the Barbie world
